'--db=[]:DB:_files' \
'--agent-id=[Agent identifier used for store operations. If unset, an NHI-hardened default is synthesized (see \`ai-memory store --help\`). Accepts the \`AI_MEMORY_AGENT_ID\` environment variable as a fallback]:AGENT_ID:_default' \
